From de4139cc7466501726ed01206df7dc19d1c21a99 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Raghavendran Madhavan <raghmadh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Sep 2025 17:55:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:PLATFORM:wifi:ath12k: Update minidump unregister call

Adding changes for the below,

- Update minidump unregister call from the beginning of the
core_deinit call to the end of it.
This is to avoid unregistering minidump related segments
before the rmmod completed.

- Adding the fw_recovery_support flag to avoid invoking the
minidump trigger when recovery is disabled.
If recovery is disabled the minidump won't be collected when
a target assert occurs, it will be collect from U-boot
only when the dump_minimal U-boot env variable is set.

- Adding changes to fix the compilation issue when MEMDEBUG
flag is enabled.

Signed-off-by: Raghavendran Madhavan <raghmadh@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 .../ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_debugfs.c       |  3 ++-
 .../wireless/ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_mem.c  |  9 +--------
 .../wireless/ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_mem.h  |  1 +
 .../ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_minidump.c      | 12 +++++++++++-
 .../ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_minidump.h      | 11 ++++++++++-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/athdbg_if.c     |  3 +--
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/athdbg_if.h     |  1 -
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/core.c          | 17 +++++++++++++----
 8 files changed, 39 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_debugfs.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/ath_debug/athdbg_debugfs.c
